                                       C Language
What is a Language..?
Sol: A Language is a communication channels between two persons...
Example: Telugu, Hindi, English, Tamil...etc..,,...
  Computer language is also a communication channel between the person and the system or electronic device...
 Languages we have to follow or know grammar and how to form a sentence...
 Computer language we have to form some programs softwares...
What is the need of computer language..?
Sol: User:: High level language(english language)
       System:: Machine language(binary language(0's or1's))
 
